The small chain, 30 mm
The main chain, 21 inches

Vintage-style, whimiscal with a gothic touch.

The heart measures 22 mm
The tour eiffel charm 28 mm
The main chain 20 inches (finishes with lobster clasp)
The shorter chain 3.5 inches

name: promenade necklace
description:

The setting measures 18 mm and the chain is 16 inches long.

Promenade will be shipped from Greece within 3 days from paypal confirmed payment and will arrive safely in a giftbox.

Sonatina will be shipped from Greece with registered mail and will arrive carefully kept in a giftbox. I ship worldwide.
